<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
      <%= @form.t(["courses", "heading"]) %>
    </h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      In order to claim a targeted retention incentive payment, you must be directly employed by the FE provider where you work.
      You can not be employed through an agency or subsidiary of the FE provider, or as a contractor.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      For more information, check the eligibility criteria for <%= govuk_link_to t("further_education_payments.eligibility_criteria_link.text"), t("further_education_payments.eligibility_criteria_link.url"), new_tab: true %>.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      If you are unsure your information is correct, you can <%= govuk_link_to "go back", claim_path(current_journey_routing_name, navigator.previous_slug) %> and review your answers. You can also <%= govuk_link_to "start the application again", claim_path(current_journey_routing_name, "landing-page") %>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
